{
  "name": "Areas",
  "summary": "<p>没有单数 Area 对象; Areas 集合的各个成员是 Range 对象。在 Areas 集合中，选定区域内每个离散的连续单元格区域都有一个 Range 对象。如果选定区域内只有一个子区域，则 Areas 集合包含一个与该选定区域对应的 Range 对象。</p>\n<p>使用 Range 对象的 Areas 属性可返回 Areas 集合。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例如果当前选定区域包含多个子区域，就清除该选定区域。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Areas</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span> !== <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Clear</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>使用 Areas (索引) （其中 index 是区域索引号）从集合中返回单个 Range 对象。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例检查当前选定区域是否为多重选定区域，如果是，则清除其中的第一个子区域的内容*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Areas</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span> !== <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Areas</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Clear</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例设置 Sheet1 上选定区域内部颜色。此示例还将检测选定区域中是否包含多重选定区域，如果包含，则对多重选定区域中每一子区域进行循环并设置内部颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Activate</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> areasCount = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Areas</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (areasCount &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= areasCount; i++) {\n            <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Areas</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>)\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>由选定区域内的多个子区域或连续单元格块组成的集合。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.Application\">Application</a>**对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.Application\">Application</a>**对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Count",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Long</strong> 值，它代表集合中对象的数量。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示 Sheet1 上选定区域中的列数。此示例还将检测选定区域中是否包含多重选定区域，如果包含，则对多重选定区域中每一子区域进行循环*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Activate</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> areasCount = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Areas</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (areasCount &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;The selection contains &quot;</span> + <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Columns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span> + <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot; columns.&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= areasCount; i++) {\n            <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Area &quot;</span> + i + <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot; of the selection contains &quot;</span> + <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Areas</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Columns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span> + <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot; columns.&quot;</span>)\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Item",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>从集合中返回一个对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例检查当前选定区域是否为多重选定区域，如果是，则清除其中的第一个子区域的内容*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Areas</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span> !== <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Areas</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Clear</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示当前选定区域的第二个子区域的单元格数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Areas</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Index",
          "type": "number（int4 精度）",
          "description": "<p>对象的索引号。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        }
      ],
      "returns": "Range"
    }
  ]
}